'''''Ndabaramukije!''''', ni Sinema ya Namibiya yasohotse muri 2017 iyobowe na Philippe Talavera kandi yakozwe nka firime ya Ombetja Yehinga (OYO).   Irimo Adriano Visagie, Odile Muller, David Ndjavera mu nshingano zabo hamwe na Monray Garoëb . Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Carlito 'Kado', wakatiwe igifungo cy’imyaka itatu kubera uburiganya, asiga umukobwa w’umukobwa utwite kugira ngo yirwaneho ku isi. 

Filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu Kwakira 2017 mu nzu yububiko. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Ku ya 30 Ugushyingo 2019 muri Canal Olympia Ouaga 2000, i Ouagadougou, [[Burukina Faso|Burkina]] Faso, umukinnyi wa mbere Adriano Visagie yatsindiye igihembo cya Sotigui nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo.  Yatowe kandi nka filime nziza muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo muri 2018 Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards (AMVCA) ndetse no gutoranywa muri sida 2018 i Amsterdam.   

